Summary: seen a possible ufo after looking back at pictures taken of the sun
divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing in my back bedroom looking out the window, I thought the sun looked really bright and I went to get my camera to take a picture. I took 5 pictures on my iPhone of the sky, one picture after another. when I looked back at the pictures there was a green glowing orb like thing in 3 of the pictures. the first picture it was very bright and close but it seemed to become duller as it ascended towards the sky. I didn't seen the orb when i was taking the pictures because I was focusing on the sun so it wasn't until I looked back at the photos that I seen it.
